data.description: WHY WAIT FOR NEW CONSTRUCTION WHEN YOU CAN MOVE INTO THIS CUSTOM-BUILT HOME. This beautiful home sits on a cul-de-sac in the desired subdivision of Abernathy.  You are welcomed through a covered front porch into the open formal dining room with double box ceilings, double crown molding, columns, custom plantation shutters throughout and an open view to the kitchen. The great room has 12' stepped ceilings, stacked stone fireplace, with hardwood look style tile in all living spaces. The kitchen features an abundance of cabinets and granite counter space with a center island, stainless steel appliances and breakfast nook area.  The Luxurious Primary Suite features a double hop ceiling with double crown molding, a beautiful custom closet with built-ins, ensuite offers double vanity, a frameless walk-in shower and a garden tub.   3 additional bedrooms and 2 bath are tucked away on the opposite side of the home.  Step outside and enjoy the screened in back lanai and the large backyard with privacy fence, and sprinkler system. This house is ready for you "TODAY".  Located in a great neighborhood, A rated school district and close to shopping.
